[[span class="bt"]]RULESET:[[/span]] A condensed form of Ritual-7000-Warden's rules have been provided below; for a full version, personnel may consult [[[https://goblinarchives.github.io/LiminalHorror/ |this document]]].

= @@ @@

[[=]]
+ [[span style="font-size: 150%;"]]7000-Warden[[/span]]
[[span class="bt" style="font-size: 125%; display: inline-block; margin-top: -22px; z-index: 10000;"]]OFFICIAL HANDBOOK[[/span]]
[[/=]]

